[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      28[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      29[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```python
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      30[0m:[38;5;10m[49m import logging
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      31[0m:[38;5;10m[49m from decimal import Decimal
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      32[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      33[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Structured logging. Never log PHI (patient names, MRNs, specific diagnosis
